    ["how", "now", "brown", "cow?"]
        |> List.map string
        |> join line
    -- how
    -- now
    -- brown
    -- cow?

When `group` is called on a Doc containing `line` elements, the `line`s are replaced with spaces.

    ["how", "now", "brown", "cow?"]
        |> List.map string
        |> join line
        |> group
